1 information; or
2 (vii) passwords or other credentials that permit access to
3 an online or other account;
4 (B) personally identifiable financial or insurance
5 information, including nonpublic personal information
6 defined by applicable federal law; and
7 (C) any combination of data that, if accessed, disclosed,
8 modified, or destroyed without authorization of the owner
9 of the data or if lost or misused, would require notice or
